@startuml admin_sequence
!theme plain
title Admin Sequence Diagram - User Management & System Overview

actor Admin
participant "System" as sys
participant "Database" as db
participant "Notification" as notif

== Login ==
Admin -> sys: Login
sys -> db: Validate Credentials
db -> sys: Return User Data
sys -> Admin: Display Dashboard

== View System Overview ==
Admin -> sys: View System Overview
sys -> db: Query System Metrics
sys -> db: Query User Statistics
sys -> db: Query Diagnosis Data
db -> sys: Return Analytics Data
sys -> Admin: Display Charts & Statistics

== Manage Users ==
Admin -> sys: Manage Users
sys -> db: Query User List
db -> sys: Return Users
sys -> Admin: Display User Management

Admin -> sys: Create New User
sys -> db: Insert User Record
db -> sys: Confirm Creation
sys -> Admin: Success Message

Admin -> sys: Ban User
sys -> db: Update User Status (is_banned=1)
db -> sys: Confirm Update
sys -> Admin: User Banned Successfully

== Review Edit Requests ==
Admin -> sys: Review Edit Requests
sys -> db: Query Pending Requests
db -> sys: Return Request List
sys -> Admin: Display Requests

Admin -> sys: Approve Edit Request
alt First Approval
  sys -> db: Update Request Status to 'approved_for_edit'
  sys -> notif: Notify Reception User
else Final Approval
  sys -> db: Update Patient Data
  sys -> db: Update Request Status to 'approved_final'
end
db -> sys: Confirm Updates
sys -> Admin: Approval Confirmation

== Download Diagnosis Data ==
Admin -> sys: Download Images
sys -> db: Query Prediction Records
db -> sys: Return Image References
sys -> Admin: Provide Download Links

@enduml